Product description

application

This Hart meter communicator is suitable for the communication operation of most HART Protocol Intelligent Transmitter. It is compatible with most hart275, hart375, hart475 manual operators and has excellent compatibility. It can communicate with imported instruments of 11513051, EJA, abb and other Hart protocols. It is fully compatible with all kinds of intelligent pressure (temperature) transmitters produced in China. At the same time, it can also communicate with electromagnetic flowmeter, V cone flowmeter, target flowmeter, vortex flowmeter and other branches Communication operation of flowmeter with HART protocol.

Note:It should be noted that due to the different models and versions of instruments manufactured by different manufacturers, and the fact that some instruments may use encrypted protocol information, this information is not only massive but also disorderly, so we cannot list the specific corresponding brands and models one by one. We cannot pledge that our product will be compatible with any instrument you purchase.

  • ● obtain the manufacturer information of Hart instruments on site .
  • ● understand the working status and fault information of Hart instrument.
  • ● read the output current and process variables of the instrument .
  • ● obtain parameters and output values of relevant sensors.

Characteristic:

  • During on-line monitoring and communication, the modulation signal will not interrupt the 4 ~ 20mA DC signal.
  • Hart communicator can be shared with most instruments using HART communication protocol and can be used with most instruments using HART communication protocol.
  • Large screen (4 lines, 18 characters per line) is easy to operate, displayed in English, easy to set and change.

  • information self diagnosis / protection function .
  • full function communication: communication supports most flow instrument, temperature instrument and transmitter with HART Protocol.
  • large screen display: larger and clearer display interface, imported LCD screen .
  • capable of production test, diagnosis and inspection of Hart intelligent equipment .
  • Hart intelligent equipment can be configured, calibrated, diagnosed, maintained and monitored during field operation .

Note:

Because of the irreparable technical problem, the Chinese subtitles appearing please follow the above picture, YES and NO, respectively.

Wiring Diagram: Connect to an externally - powered 2 - wire HART transmitter

As the field environment where the instrument is used is usually complicated, occasionally unexpected situations may occur, if you can't connect properly, please feel free to contact u s for professional guidance, please don't make bad comments before that, thank you.

  • Your instrumentation must have an open HART protocol.
  • Please refer to the wiring diagram, usually need to connect a 250 ohm resistor.
  • If the site environment has strong magnetic field, radiation or current interference, it may cause abnormalities such as unable to connect, please move to a non-interference environment and try again.
  • If the instrument used for control has no internal power supply, please connect 24V DC power supply.
  • About the Chinese font that appears, please check the right side view.
